The brigade arrives at a village the way weather arrives — expected, unarguable, known by name — and where it vouches for your people, twenty years of official lies stop mattering for an afternoon. Coffee is weighed honestly on the brigade's scales; a cacique's overseer finds his accounts audited by teenagers with rifles and arithmetic; and the Party's organizer, introduced by the right nickname, is lent the sierra's scarcest commodity, which was never food or bullets but belief.

@escuela_sierra
title: La escuela de la sierra
subtitle: His assemblies, taught to your cadres: the war council as classroom, the column as school.
card-image: img/Lucio.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; inteligencia += 3; unity += 2; sup_teachers += 1

He never stopped being a teacher; he only changed schools. The famous assemblies — every combatant speaking in turn, every decision argued to consensus under a tarp in the rain — are also, your observers realize, the best intelligence system in Guerrero: a hundred pairs of eyes debriefed nightly by a man who grades attention. What your cadres bring down from a season with him is not doctrine. It is the habit of listening to the base as if your life depended on it, because his does.

@impuesto
title: El impuesto de guerra
subtitle: The sierra's treasury shares its sources — levies on the coffee brokers who bled the coast for decades.
card-image: img/Lucio.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0 and via = "armada"
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if advisor_action_timer = 0 : Only on the armed road does the war's treasury open to you. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; funds += 5; expediente += 4; represion += 1

The brokers who set the coffee price with one hand and the interest rate with the other have paid the sierra's tax for years — Lucio's receipts are famous, itemized, and honored, which is more than anyone says of the state's. This season a share moves through three intermediaries to your treasury. It is the cleanest dirty money in Mexico: extracted from men who stole it first, by a man who publishes his accounts to a village assembly.

